{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-016__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-016", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-016__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·016.1", "text_original": "北風其涼，雨雪其雱，\n惠而好我，攜手同行，【韻：雱行】\n其虛其邪，既亟只且。", "text_normalized": "北風其涼，雨雪其雱，\n惠而好我，攜手同行，【韻：雱行】\n其虛其邪，既亟只且。", "notes": "北風 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-016__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-016", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-016__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·016.2", "text_original": "北風其喈，雨雪其霏，\n惠而好我，攜手同歸，【韻：霏歸】\n其虛其邪，既亟只且。", "text_normalized": "北風其喈，雨雪其霏，\n惠而好我，攜手同歸，【韻：霏歸】\n其虛其邪，既亟只且。", "notes": "北風 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-beifeng-016__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-beifeng-016", "source_id": "guofeng-beifeng-016__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·邶風·016.3", "text_original": "莫赤匪狐，莫黑匪烏，\n惠而好我，攜手同車，【韻：烏車】\n其虛其邪，既亟只且。", "text_normalized": "莫赤匪狐，莫黑匪烏，\n惠而好我，攜手同車，【韻：烏車】\n其虛其邪，既亟只且。", "notes": "北風 Chinese stanza 3."}
